# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Waiting-list form → Google Sheet via Apps Script (section 11)
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the value. `.env.local` is gitignored.
# Full walkthrough: PROJECT-LOG.md → "11 — Form". Script source: apps-script/waitlist.gs
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# The Apps Script web-app URL you get after deploying apps-script/waitlist.gs.
# Looks like: https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycb.../exec
# Called server-side only — never exposed to the browser.
WAITLIST_WEBHOOK_URL=

# Shared secret sent with each webhook request. Set the SAME value as
# SHARED_SECRET in apps-script/waitlist.gs so the script can reject direct
# POSTs to its public /exec URL. Generate one with:  openssl rand -base64 24
# Optional — leave blank (and SHARED_SECRET="") to disable the check.
WAITLIST_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
